    <div class="context">
        <p>Nestled in Brgy. Sudtunggan, Basak, Lapu-Lapu City, Anami Homes Mactan is a 1.3-hectare development designed for modern and comfortable living. Located just minutes away from Mactan International Airport, Mactan Doctors Hospital, major malls, schools, resorts, and business hubs, it offers the perfect balance of convenience and tranquility.</p>
        <p>Beyond well-designed homes and top-tier amenities—including a 24/7 secured entrance, a multi-purpose hall, a covered basketball court, parks, playgrounds, and concrete roads—we’re taking community living to the next level with SubdiWise, our official community portal.</p>
        <p>With SubdiWise, residents can stay informed, connect with neighbors, receive real-time updates, and access important services—all in one place. More than just a home, Anami Homes is now a connected and thriving neighborhood, making life more seamless and secure.</p>
